{"tid":1432984,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家：現時香港並沒有就光滋擾訂立法例","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:47:20.000Z","uid":12171,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"083035a85cea161565c9154c5233d96be76cf749","tid":1432984,"uid":12171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/essentials-1819ise08-regulation-of-nuisance-caused-by-external-lighting.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fresearch-publications%2Fchinese%2Fessentials-1819ise08-regulation-of-nuisance-caused-by-external-lighting.htm&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO709C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=0ee0e607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/essentials-1819ise08-regulation-of-nuisance-caused-by-external-lighting.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對於戶外燈光滋擾問題，政府只能夠勸喻而唔可以採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n如果狗宿舍俾燈光滋擾咁點算好呀？</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148091fb6a5fc9ab7c80d94e8e7067ea2566fa56","tid":1432984,"uid":294614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"8.9       機場萬人接機<br />\n開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區<br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n少你一個真係少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日 機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGQPZ5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGQPZ5c.png&h=7a7f7945&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8f7fc3d5f22a90